(0)



















by
krisdagrk
Sep 03, 2010


Good reading about the invasion of Iraq from 1st POV
I bought this book after watching the mini series Generation Kill.  The mini series was really entertaining the book is more straight forward of what actually happened to the 1st battalion recon team during the invasion of Iraq.  Some very interesting things were noted.  A good read.

